user_shop_relationship_with_toppings_limit:
Each shop must define its own set of available toppings and the maximum number of toppings allowed for each product or order.

product_category_and_pricing_rules:
All products are required to belong to a product category and must include a unit price, an optional discounted price, and support for add-on toppings with individual prices.

topping_price_configurable_per_product:
The price for each topping can be configured per product or per shop, allowing customization for different items.

enforce_maximum_topping_count_per_order:
The system must check and prevent users from selecting more toppings than the shop's configured maximum for a product or order.
